{"word":"ἐπιμειδάω","slug":"ἐπιμειδάω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n40139\" key=\"e)pimeida/w\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">ἐπιμειδ-άω</orth>, <sense id=\"n40139.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">smile at</tr_> or <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">upon</tr_>, in <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Hom.</author> </bibl> always in phrase, <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">τὸν δ᾽</foreign> <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἐπιμειδήσας προσέφη</foreign> he addressed him <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">with a smile</tr_>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:4:356\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">4.356</biblScope></bibl>, al.; in <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:10:400\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">10.400</biblScope></bibl>, of a scornful smile; but <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ἦκ᾽ ἐπιμειδήσας</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0020.tlg001.perseus-grc1:547\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Hes.\">Hes.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Th.\">Th.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">547</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>: c.dat., <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"title\">AP</title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">6.345</biblScope> </bibl> (<bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Crin.</author> </bibl>).</sense> </entryFree>"}]}